xtras/bfb20786106e5db332ff387ab592bbee.avif?t=1741772393\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/210f74c5914f78d7ec3616137de378f8.poster.avif?t=1741772393\" width=540 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/210f74c5914f78d7ec3616137de378f8.webm?t=1741772393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/210f74c5914f78d7ec3616137de378f8.mp4?t=1741772393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
